# Bovie Architecture & Structure Rules

## Feature Structure Pattern

Each feature in `ui/` MUST follow this structure:

```
ui/feature_name/
├── domain/              # Repository interface (if persistence needed)
│   └── feature_repository.dart
├── data/                # Repository implementation (if persistence needed)
│   └── feature_repository_impl.dart
└── presentation/        # UI + Stores + Feature-specific widgets
    ├── feature_screen.dart
    ├── feature_store.dart
    └── widgets/         # Optional feature-specific widgets
```

## Examples

### Onboarding Feature
```
ui/onboarding/
├── domain/
│   └── onboarding_repository.dart
├── data/
│   └── onboarding_repository_impl.dart
└── presentation/
    ├── onboarding_movies_screen.dart
    ├── onboarding_movies_store.dart
    ├── onboarding_genres_screen.dart
    └── onboarding_genres_store.dart
```

### Paywall Feature
```
ui/paywall/
└── presentation/
    ├── paywall_screen_a.dart
    ├── paywall_screen_b.dart
    ├── paywall_store.dart
    └── widgets/
        ├── feature_comparison_table.dart
